data.value: Game Rules: -Players must place their marks on an empty square. -A square that already contains an "X" or "O" cannot be chosen again. -The game ends when either player achieves three marks in a row, or all squares are filled resulting in a draw. -Players must alternate turns. The same player cannot make two consecutive moves. -If the game ends (either with a winner or a draw), players can choose to reset the board and start a new round.
